Facilities at Ideo Verve are great and are offering a large swimming pool jacuzzi fitness keycard system parking and 24 hour security. Basically everything is close by easy walk to the BTS station and crossing the BTS station will bring you to the mall with the Tesco Lotus McDonalds KFC MK restaurant and many more shops.
